      "rationale": "All model inputs (fluid viscosity, density, pump geometry, rotational speed, inlet flow rate) characterized with measured distributions. Monte Carlo propagation of input uncertainties performed with 2000 samples. 95th-percentile hemolysis prediction remains below clinical threshold.",
