        "description": "All primary model inputs must have documented uncertainty distributions based on measurement data. UQ propagation must demonstrate that 95th-percentile QoI prediction remains below acceptance threshold. Achieved: all 6 primary inputs characterized; P95 NIH = 0.0031 g/100L vs threshold 0.0050 g/100L."
